In 300-synthesis.md, discuss the interdisciplinary blend of concepts
from genetics, computer science, and mathematics that are used in the
design of PromiseGrid.  Consider the implications if a sequence letter
can be any arbitary byte value from 0x00 to 0xff.  Discuss the impact
of such a design on the storage of hashed data, raw data, module
hashes, module argument parameters, and how received messages are
processed.  

